channel.title: Almost at the point of punching someone!
channel.description:
I have tried so many things to get my server on the status page! It always says it is offline. I have done everything the tutorials say!
Here are the specs:
Server: Allstar-scape V2. Java: jdk1.6.0_07, jre1.6.0_07, jre1.6.0_01. Name: shelshockscape.no-ip.info . IP: I used the one NO-IP gave me. Firewall: Allowed shelshockscape.no-ip.info. Port - 43594. Protocol - TCP Router: Linksys: Application: Moparscape. Start - 43594 to End - 43594. Protocol - TCP IP address - 192.168.1.1 Additional information: I opened the Runserver thing. Then tried to register it... Nothing. I also Have the NO-IP DUC downloaded and the guy is blushing with my Server name on there.
What do I do!?
